name: Google Cloud Dataproc
description: Use Google Cloud Dataproc, an Apache Hadoop, Apache Spark, Apache Pig, and Apache Hive service, to easily process big datasets at low cost. Control your costs by quickly creating managed clusters of any size and turning them off when youre done. Cloud Dataproc integrates across Google Cloud Platform products, giving you a powerful and complete data processing platform.
